##Non-hubei area appears the unusual rebound, overseas new case first surpasses the domestic

Micro-signal Huolibuluo

Function introduction, linkage three medicine, bridge capital, direct health

There were 24 new cases in non-hubei areas of the country on the 25th, including 10 cases in Beijing. The number of medical observers, new suspected cases and upstream data such as pending investigation of suspected cases continued to decline steadily in these areas, the sharp rebound in the data should be an anomaly.

Cumulative confirmed cases: the total number of cases is expected to control around 80,000

As of 24:00 on February 26,31 provinces (autonomous regions, municipalities directly under the Central Government) and Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps had reported 78,497 new cases of pneumonia and 433 new cases.

Figure 1

2. New Cases: Abnormal rebound in Beijing, Zhangjiakou, etc. 

Figure 2

Non-hubei areas of 25 new cases of 24, including 10 cases in Beijing, a sharp rebound. The sharp rebound is unusual, given the steady decline in the number of medical observers, new suspected cases and upstream data on the list of suspected cases. According to the information released by Beijing Health Commission, the 10 cases were all diagnosed by close contacts of the cases announced in Beijing on February 25. There are also large rebound in Zhangjiakou City, Hebei (5 cases) , GarzÃª Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture, Sichuan (3 cases) and so on, from the previous Hubei Wuhan several abnormal data fluctuations, the possibility of carrying out a certain inventory of cases digestion. We look forward to further information and explanation from relevant parties.

Figure 3

Although the overall decline in Hubei non-wuhan areas, but Xiaogan appeared in 15 cases, it is worthy of attention.

Figure 4

Wuhan's numbers seem to suggest that it is digesting yet another small Landslide dam. According to reader Liu Yang, there are three core reasons why the Wuhan data have fluctuated over the last few days, rather than falling, in a flat period:

1 Wuhan is short of resources for a long time, which makes the scope of "close contacts" narrow, about 1:4, while the area outside Wuhan has long been as high as 1:30 or more. Now that the resources have come up, there is a new round of screening;

2 The ability of grass-roots organizations in different communities is different. Before this, some local people in Wuhan frequently complained that their neighborhood had not been checked. In this part, they had to pull the net again to check, this will result in a concentration of newly confirmed cases in some regions at one time;

3 there should be only a minimal probability of secondary transmission due to the inadequate closure of the former residential area, such as the problem of individual small shops. From field experience, this part of the factor is difficult to affect the big data pool, but it is managed like a needle in a haystack, it's hard not to be overly strict.

In summary, reader Liu Yang predicts that barring a single thunderstorm, there will be a significant drop in the number of confirmed cases in Wuhan in the near future. In the same way, the 15 newly confirmed cases in Xiaogan today may be a similar reason, as the largest number of people returned to their homes in the early stages, leading to too wide a scope for suspected and close contacts, thus extending the second screening window. Xiao Bian agrees with reader Liu Yang's interpretation.

6. Number of people in hospital: Continue to release medical resources, the situation of resources in Wuhan has been completely reversed

10

The stock of people treated in hospitals has declined and hospital beds continue to be released on a large scale. The presumed number of people in Hubei who were diagnosed but not hospitalized also continued to decline.

The case fatality rate is slowly rising, and the cure rate is rising even faster

Figure 11

The case fatality rate (CFR) has been increasing slowly since early February, which basically accords with the normal characteristics of CFR in epidemic situation. But in Hubei, especially in Wuhan, there are also factors that can not be put in place. February 24, the Central Working Leading Group Meeting to respond to the epidemic of new pneumonia, in particular, Wuhan to implement classified admission measures to make maximum efforts to reduce the case fatality rate. Recently, the central government has stepped up the implementation of a series of measures to strengthen the rescue capacity, at the meeting of the Central Leading Group on the response to the epidemic of NCP on February 24, it was further emphasized that Wuhan should further implement measures of screening and classified admission and treatment, and comprehensively improve its treatment capacity, we will do our best to raise the cure rate and reduce the mortality rate, increase the treatment of severe and critically ill patients, push forward the treatment of mild patients, and prevent mild cases from turning into severe cases. It can be inferred from the rapid decline in the rate of severe cases that a series of measures to strengthen the treatment are making great changes in the treatment situation around, especially in Wuhan.

There were 557 new cases overseas, exceeding the number at home for the first time

Summary: The new cases in non-hubei areas in China have rebounded remarkably, and the new cases in overseas areas have surpassed the domestic for the first time. Looks like the small make up wants to leave the class early the wish also had to defer a few days.

With 505 confirmed and 11 removed from their posts, how can prisons prevent an outbreak?
As of 2400 hours on February 20, five prisons in Hubei, Zhejiang and Shandong had reported outbreaks of new coronavirus infection, all of which were imported cases. Of the 505 confirmed cases, no deaths had been reported.
Dialogue Yang Gonghuan: It is very likely that the new coronavirus will coexist with humans for a long time

ABIDOL and chloroquine phosphate are still needed to be tested in clinical trials for the treatment of new coronary pneumonia. Clinical trials of the drugs should continue even after the outbreak is over, to prevent a relapse.

TAKATOMI RESPONDS TO CONTROVERSY: Can't fight on the Internet, working on a cunning virus
TAKATOMI's previous claims have been challenged by the new pneumonia outbreak, which has now surpassed SARS in both confirmed cases and deaths. Whether Takatomi and the CDC "failed in their duty" is at the center of the controversy.

Who was the first person to be genetically tested for new coronavirus pneumonia?

Two new cases of coronary pneumonia with pathology results are available, and the autopsy is still under way
Researchers are trying to reveal the pathogenicity and lethality of the new coronavirus and provide new evidence for clinical treatment. The phase result is that the pathogenicity of the new coronavirus is similar to SARS, and the further result may be revealed by dissection.

Analysis of 70,000 new coronary disease cases: crude case-fatality rate 2.3% 
So far, there is no evidence of a superspreader event like the SARS outbreak, but the exact cause of the infection and the failure to prevent remains to be investigated.
